# Data files (too large for git, or licensed and not redistributable).
# The trailing bare "data/" rule this block used to end with silently ignored
# the whole data/ directory regardless of the negations below it (git applies
# rules in order — a later blanket rule re-excludes anything a negation above
# it un-ignored) — meaning the small curated pipeline inputs below were never
# actually tracked. Fixed: blanket-ignore by extension, then explicitly keep
# the handful of small, essential, hand-curated CSVs a fresh clone needs to
# run the simulator at all.
*.csv
*.mmdb
!data/wifi/wigle_sample.csv
!data/device_posture/device_posture.csv
!data/tls/ja3_fingerprints.csv
!data/rba/rba_sample.csv

# Large external raw datasets (downloaded separately, not redistributed —
# see updated/reference_material/citations_rba_dataset.md for how to obtain
# them). Includes CIC-IDS2018 (~1.2GB) and the raw RBA dataset zip (~1GB) —
# only the small filtered rba_sample.csv above is tracked.
datasets/

# Thesis manuscript itself — kept local-only. This is a public repo; the
# code, figures, and reference material documenting real results are fine
# to share, but the in-progress unpublished manuscript is not.
updated/*.docx


